dialogue.text: How much longer do we have to wait? We told her the truth and that should've activated the rumor right?
Finally, some good news! lets get started and rally up the feathers.
Someone seperated the rumor from the hostess, we're still missing a Maiden.
Ugghh! Are you telling those little imbeciles at the subway removed our brainwashing!?
I thought our hostess had a faint heart and couldn't be easily broken.
She does, someone must of have had the magic to remove it and calm her down.
And you had to tell the hostess out hideout?
How would I know that this would happen!
I'll send over some feathers to watch over them and report anything valuable.
Make sure they don't ever lose sight on the one who tampered our hostess.
I don't want any news of that boy I'll direct the feathers to you. He is already a nusiance to look at.
